  "detailed_description": "Joltzsi (Jolt-see) is an addictive action puzzle game building off classic predecessors such as Columns, Puyo Puyo and Tetris.<br>Its \"stacking\" feature adds a unique strategic twist to the block-falling genre.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/f13dcba1dbc08f6d55988e0c683272a8.poster.avif?t=1747779554\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/f13dcba1dbc08f6d55988e0c683272a8.webm?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/f13dcba1dbc08f6d55988e0c683272a8.mp4?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Layer \"falling\" tetrominoes on top of each other increasing values from 1 to 4.<br></li><li> Clears lines with vertical and horizontal matches.<br></li><li> <strong>Score Big</strong> with higher values and multiple lines BUT pieces can fall fast, and going above 4 is \"Game Over\".</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/f7490284ffc0dd307a67369784e26443.webp?t=1747779554\" width=286 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/31498d65024cb32de256b5ad0aea4332.poster.avif?t=1747779554\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/31498d65024cb32de256b5ad0aea4332.webm?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/31498d65024cb32de256b5ad0aea4332.mp4?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Try to make the highest possible clear, a 4 line 4 height <strong>Joltzsi</strong> 4 <strong>MAX POINTS</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/6394b1d1f8e0ef98f09227b7cb2d8d82.webp?t=1747779554\" width=286 height=52 /></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/0577efce177af374c018257b5596e422.poster.avif?t=1747779554\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/0577efce177af374c018257b5596e422.webm?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/0577efce177af374c018257b5596e422.mp4?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Enjoy multiple game modes and options<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Advanced Mode</strong> with multi-valued pieces<br></li><li> <strong>Glitched Mode</strong> with a series of unique rules throughout perpetual play<br></li><li> <strong>Competitive</strong> Online PVP Battles Mode, Seasons and Tournaments<br></li><li> <strong>Special On-Fire Edition DLC</strong> featuring the <strong>Voice of NBA Jam</strong> Tim Kitzrow!  <br></li><li> And several more modes!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/8e81a33782f426636737700da7eebbbe.webp?t=1747779554\" width=286 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/5b2f0b761a19455be08e54df356bd050.avif?t=1747779554\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br>Be the leader by:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Having the highest score (All Time, Monthly, Weekly]<br></li><li> Competing in regular seasons and tournaments <br></li><li> Winning in PVP and Battle Mode<br></li><li> Being among the first to accomplish something with <strong> several stats being tracked for all-time </strong></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/4b04a71d13f2e1f5968b85a4c3964d79.webp?t=1747779554\" width=286 height=52 /></span><br>Joltzsi was designed to be an deep yet easy to pick up and play game perfect when you're on the go!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/b38ccb20b510c8fbb0b960f30d1cb060.poster.avif?t=1747779554\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/b38ccb20b510c8fbb0b960f30d1cb060.webm?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560390/extras/b38ccb20b510c8fbb0b960f30d1cb060.mp4?t=1747779554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
